unittitle_ssm: New York University Archives Collection on Commencement Celebrations Webpages
abstract_ssm: New York University Archives Collection on  Commencement Celebrations Webpages documents the commencement proceedings for New York University and its school ceremonies. The collection was established in response to the COVID-19 pandemic. The collection contains video streams of the ceremonies, awards, student profiles, messages from deans, names of graduates, and commencement programs.
